'''Bwana Mkuu''' was  Sultan of [[Pate Island#Pate Town|Pate]], [[Kenya]], 1688 to 1713. At the time Pate dominated [[Lamu]]. Bwana Mkuu set up residency at Lamu, complete with a Lamu lady as one of his wives and a private [[mosque]].<ref>Martin, 1973, p. 7</ref>

